description:
Is it flowers or colorful leaves I didn't know. 
It was my birthday. I was happy. I jumped into the sea from a high pier. For so many years I have fought to experience this: feel happy with myself and at the same time forget about everything, accept my imperfections, but know that everything has its place. Maybe I've become an adult. But for the most part of my current happiness I'm grateful to the HEN community.
